# ==============================================================================
# ArchSpine Semantic Ignore Configuration
# ==============================================================================
# [English]
# Purpose: Fine-tune the AI's "reading scope". Exclude files tracked by Git 
# that provide no architectural value, saving tokens and reducing AI hallucinations.
# 
# Notes:
# - Auto-inherits .gitignore (do not repeat node_modules, dist, etc.).
# - Internal .spine/ files (like cache.db) are automatically shielded.
#
# Examples:
# 1. Tracked by Git, but ignore for AI (Reduce noise)
# benchmarks/data/
# tests/fixtures/large-snapshots/
# src/locales/generated-*.json
# *.svg
# 
# 2. Ignored by Git, but include for AI (Recall context)
# !vendor/our-patches/
# !.env.example

# ==============================================================================
# ArchSpine 语义忽略配置
# ==============================================================================
# [中文]
# 核心定位：微调 AI 的“代码阅读范围”。排除已提交到 Git 但对 AI 理解架构毫无帮助的
# 噪音文件，从而节省 Token 并减少 AI 幻觉。
#
# 注意事项：
# - 自动继承 .gitignore（无需重复添加 node_modules、dist 等）。
# - 系统自动屏蔽 .spine/ 内部缓存文件（如 cache.db）。
#
# 配置示例：
# 1. Git 已跟踪，但 AI 不该阅读（减少噪音）
# benchmarks/data/
# tests/fixtures/large-snapshots/
# src/locales/generated-*.json
# *.svg
#
# 2. Git 已忽略，但 AI 需要阅读（特殊召回）
# !vendor/our-patches/
# !.env.example

# >>> ArchSpine repo-specific >>>
# Specific to ArchSpine development: exclude large external test corpora and coverage reports.
research/bench/corpus/
coverage/
# <<< ArchSpine repo-specific <<<

# >>> ArchSpine recommended >>>
# Recommended semantic exclusions for high-noise, low-information local and generated content.
# Human-facing repository docs usually already have an authoritative readable form.
# Edit or remove these suggestions if they are intentional architecture inputs in this repository.

# Common local secrets
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.crt
*.cer

# Common generated, cache, and runtime noise not worth indexing by default
.next/
.nuxt/
.svelte-kit/
.parcel-cache/
.turbo/
.cache/
tmp/
temp/
__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.tox/
.venv/
venv/
target/

# Common semantic-noise outputs
docs/
README.md
README.en.md
README.zh-CN.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
SECURITY.md
SUPPORT.md
CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
docs/.vitepress/dist/
externaldocs/

# Keep repository automation and control-plane inputs indexable by default
!schemas/
!.github/workflows/
# <<< ArchSpine recommended <<<
